            "text": "Out-of-bounds write in update_setting(): the index 'i' parsed from user input is checked against SETTINGS_COUNT but never checked for i < 0. A negative index (e.g. \"-7\") computes an address before setting[0] in the struct, landing on the isAdmin field and allowing a non-admin user to escalate privileges."
          },
