          "level": "error",
          "message": {
            "text": "Mutable internal method reference in CryptoAPI.sha1.hash(): the call CryptoAPI.sha1._round(H, w) resolves _round via a public, non-frozen property. Any external code can overwrite CryptoAPI.sha1._round with a malicious function that will be executed on the next hash() call. Fix by capturing a local reference (var internalRound = API.sha1._round) and calling that instead."
          },
