          "level": "error",
          "message": {
            "text": "Prototype pollution via uninitialized array in CryptoAPI.sha1.hash(): 'w' is declared as an empty array ([]). Writes to w[0..127] can trigger malicious setters injected into Array.prototype before the library loads (e.g. via Array.prototype.__defineSetter__). Fix by pre-initializing w with all 128 elements explicitly so own properties shadow any prototype setters."
          },
