          "message": {
            "text": "Unsafe regular expression in generateRegex(): the function joins every character of the secret with .* (e.g. A.*B.*C.*...) and applies it with RegExp. Against a long model response that almost-but-not-quite matches, the engine backtracks exponentially. With longer secrets the worst-case time grows rapidly. Use a linear-time string search instead of a generated regex."
